      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a dream! I've taken great care of it, so it's ready to hit the road with you today. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. Come check it out!",
