    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerhouse delivers 414 hp with a razor-sharp 8,400 RPM redline, channeled through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the weight-saving carbon fiber roof panel which significantly lowers the center of gravity. Recent preventative maintenance includes addressed rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems operate at peak efficiency. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a driven machine, the longitudinal dynamics and hydraulic steering rack feedback remain uncompromised. This is a purist-spec E92 ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 31500.0,
