      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up stone chip on the hood\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health with a documented history of on-time oil changes and recent brake service. It handles precisely, shifts smoothly, and sits on a set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a dependable, turnkey example that looks great in a driveway and performs reliably on the road.",
